document_data.name: Cart Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Cart Street''' was a small street found in the town of [[New Velar|Harrowdale]].
document_data.Description: Cart Street branched off of the southern end of [[Melurk Street]] at [[The Lady of Good Fortune]]. The street passed southeast through town to end at [[Harrow Plow Pier]] on the [[Dragon Reach]].
